plot: Supergirl and the super friends take drastic action after a loved one is kidnapped by Nyxly and Lex; an unlikely ally steps in to help the team.

After taking Esme prisoner, Nxyly and Lex have a difference of opinion on how to remove the Love Totem from the girl. Meanwhile, the Super Friends come up with a plan to supercharge Supergirl so that she can take on the villains, and Alex makes a different decision.—Gislef
